title: Avalon - Official Teaser Trailer
description:
Avalon is an MMORPG game built by the players developed by Avalon Corp. Players can explore new worlds, conquer dungeons, craft equipment, battle in PVP, level up, collect rare items, and craft new experiences for others all using the power of Unreal Engine. From lush forested lands wielding swords and spells to a gritty cyberpunk city with nothing but guns to dispatch enemies, Avalon is a community-created experience by the players. Avalon is launching on PC at a later date.

title: Dark and Darker Mobile - Official Gameplay Reveal Trailer
description:
Dark and Darker Mobile is a mobile fantasy extraction RPG game developed by Krafton. Players will go on a journey into a PvPvE experience where they will dispatch cunning adventurers and monsters while exploring dungeons consumed by darkness. Hidden treasure containing unparalleled wealth and power awaits players brave enough to pursue it as they delve deeper into the game. Dark and Darker Mobile is launching in 2024 for iOS and Android.
